    public static class MORAxioms.AxiomsBase<T>
extends java.util.HashSet<T>
implements Semantic.Axioms<T>
    The base interface for all the MORAxioms that extends Axioms or SemanticAxioms.

    This class implements common features for managing an HashSet and a singleton value for Semantic.Axioms.
